      "name": "Primary QoI comparison: FEA vs. bench test N=11",
      "description": "FEA predictions of construct stiffness (N/mm), yield force (N), and force at 40 mm displacement (N) compared against experimental measurements from 11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol. All three QoIs satisfy the <10% mean difference acceptance criterion. The validation metric E/uval remains below 1.96 for each QoI, confirming that model error is within combined experimental and model uncertainty bounds.",
      "validationMetric": "E/uval < 1.96 for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement; mean QoI difference < 10%",
      "comparisonOutcome": "Pass",
