      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under an FDA-recognized quality management system. Solver version locked and hash-verified. Regression tests for SOLID186 and CONTA174 elements pass without exception. QA records archived in the study master file."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
