      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and ASME V&V 10 suite reproduced within 1% of analytical solution for linear elastic beam bending and contact patch test.",
      "rationale": "Three NAFEMS benchmarks (LE1, LE10, and contact patch test) executed with the production solver configuration. Maximum deviation from analytical reference is 0.4%. Code verification is considered adequate for the linear-elastic, small-deformation regime of the F1717 test."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
